    "slide-1-the-economic-structural-reality.md": "Economic structure reached $5.2 trillion in 2024 while practice consolidation accelerated.",
    "slide-2-the-human-cost-system-waste-burnout.md": "About 25% of healthcare spending goes to administrative costs and waste. Burnout is a system design problem.",
